\doxysubsection{Detailed Description}
\hypertarget{newton__control_8h_newton_control_api_sec}{}\doxysubsection{Newton Control A\+PI}\label{newton__control_8h_newton_control_api_sec}
\hypertarget{newton__control_8h_api_intro_sec}{}\doxysubsection{Newton Control A\+PI}\label{newton__control_8h_api_intro_sec}
The purpose of the Newton Control A\+PI is to provide an A\+PI for controlling the Newton from a host processor via the S\+PI Slave interface of the Newton.\hypertarget{newton__control_8h_functions_sec}{}\doxysubsection{Summary of Functionality}\label{newton__control_8h_functions_sec}
The following is a summary of funcionality provided by the Newton Control A\+PI\+:


\begin{DoxyItemize}
\item Reset H\+SP
\item S\+PI read
\item S\+PI write
\item register read
\item register write
\item Load fuses from file
\item Load H\+SP R\+OM from file
\item Load program into newton memory from file
\item Unload fuses to file
\item Unload H\+SP R\+OM to file
\item Unload program from newton memory to file
\item Verify fuses against file contents
\item Verify H\+SP R\+OM against file contents
\item Verify program in newton memory against file contents
\end{DoxyItemize}\hypertarget{newton__control_8h_examples_sec}{}\doxysubsection{Code examples}\label{newton__control_8h_examples_sec}
